## Proposed Changes

### Priority 1 — UI Surface: The Matrix Comes Alive

---

#### [MODIFY] [IdeologyCompass.tsx](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/ui/src/app/components/IdeologyCompass.tsx)

**Current state:** 96 lines. Props: `authoritarianLibertarian`, `plannedMarket`, `overtonRadius`. Does not receive Phase 16 fields.

**Required prop extensions:**
```typescript
interface IdeologyCompassProps {
    // Existing
    authoritarianLibertarian: number;
    plannedMarket: number;
    overtonRadius: number;
    // Phase 17 additions
    positionHistory?: [number, number][];     // IDX-011 breadcrumb trail
    perceivedPosition?: [number, number];     // IDX-010 Deep State Delta
    flavorLabel?: string;                     // IDX-005 real label
    perceivedFlavorLabel?: string;            // IDX-010 perceived label
    velocityShock?: boolean;                  // IDX-009 shock flash trigger
    veilGap?: number;                         // Gap for coloring the tension line
}
```

**Visual additions:**
1. **Breadcrumb Comet** — 10 fading dots from `positionHistory`. Oldest: opacity 0.05, newest: 0.7. Color: `amber-accent/60`.
2. **Deep State Delta** — `perceivedPosition` as hollow glowing ring. Real [position](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/brinkmanship_engine/src/scenario.rs#232-248) stays solid amber crosshair. Tension line between them: orange at gap > 2.5, `#FF2222` at gap > 3.5 (Veil Collapse).
3. **Dual Flavor Labels** — Hover overlay: `LABEL:` + `PERCEIVED:` (dimmer, italic). Only shown when they differ.
4. **Velocity Shock Banner** — `⚡ POLITICAL SHOCK` flash, `AnimatePresence`, 2s duration, CRT scanline distortion overlay.

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/ui/src/app/page.tsx)

Extend state fetch to pass `position_history`, `perceived_position`, `perceived_flavor_label`, [flavor_label](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/brinkmanship_engine/src/ideology_matrix.rs#98-123), `position_velocity` from `/state` API as props to [IdeologyCompass](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/ui/src/app/components/IdeologyCompass.tsx#12-94).

