## Game Mode Architecture Note

Per V18 directive, `legislation.rs` and [state.rs](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/brinkmanship_engine/src/state.rs) additions should be structured to eventually support:
- **Deep State Mode**: Player IS the permanent bureaucracy; administrations change via Election Algorithm
- **Politician Mode**: Player IS the administration; 4–8 year electoral clock; `perceived_flavor_label` must match median voter

Both modes share the same engine physics. Mode is a runtime flag, not an architectural split.
